text: Oberpframmern is a community in the Upper Bavarian district of Ebersberg and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (administrative community) of Glonn. It is about 24 kilometres southeast of Munich. ==Geography== Oberpframmern is in the Munich Region.
